Load .rds file from a remote connection

Source: R/from_url.R
rds_from_url.Rd

Load .rds file from a remote connection

Usage

rds_from_url(url)

Arguments

url

a character url

Value

a dataframe as created by readRDS()

Examples

# \donttest{
rds_from_url("https://github.com/nflverse/nfldata/raw/master/data/games.rds")
